name: Gearbreed
desc: During your Draw Phase, instead of conducting your Draw, you can: Add 1 Equip Spell from your Deck or GY to your hand. If you control an Equip Spell: You can return 1 FIRE Warrior monster or Gemini monster from your GY to the bottom of your Deck; draw 1 card. You can only use each effect of "Gearbreed" once per turn.
